text: Margaret Rogers or Maggie Rogers may refer to: *Maggie Rogers (White House maid) (1874–1953), American staff member *Margaret Rogers (nurse) (1875–1915), New Zealand WWI casualty *Margaret Rogers (politician) (born 1949), American state legislator in Mississippi *Maggie Rogers (born 1994), American performer ==See also== *Margaret Rodgers (disambiguation)
title: Margaret Rogers
